  "2365790": {
    "name": "Let's Build a Dungeon",
    "steam_appid": 2365790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用你自己的方式运营一家游戏工作室并观察事态如何发展，一切尽在这款出自《Let’s Build a Zoo》创作者之手的多层次管理模拟游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/3f0ffcf60f20298ec5dbd40f14fd2d03.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/e0a5aeb300d4cbbf3499a9e7e9e62853.poster.avif?t=1771980246\" width=780 height=249 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/e0a5aeb300d4cbbf3499a9e7e9e62853.webm?t=1771980246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在这款写实而荒谬的游戏产业模拟游戏中，审阅数以百计有望入职的申请者的简历，为你的梦想工作室招兵买马。 招募并管理美术师、程序员和策划师，打造新的资产和机制，为你的创作赋予生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理开发时间表、广告宣传活动和媒体关系，将你的工作室从一个充满斗志的独立团队发展成一家开发巨擎。 你会冒着破产的风险推迟游戏发布，直至它达到完美状态吗？或者以加班和减薪将你的员工逼迫至濒临崩溃？ 你会屈服于社区要求，还是忠实于自己的创意愿景？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/3f6199e753a7b0ab77fa268c8afd07a5.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/d9b768fc50d87e2343fecfb930df75ca.poster.avif?t=1771980246\" width=780 height=249 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/d9b768fc50d87e2343fecfb930df75ca.webm?t=1771980246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>作为一个缺乏经验的MMORPG开发者，你的职责是打造一个奇幻世界，在平衡收支的同时让虚拟玩家流连忘返。 欢迎他们进入你的世界，并看着他们展开冒险之旅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计一场内容广阔的冒险之旅，在其中加入任务、城市、怪物和地宫，满足你的虚拟玩家的个性化需求。 随时跃入游戏中封禁不守规矩的用户，并从一个新视角观察你的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能用一款RPG经典游戏震撼你的受众吗？又或者这款游戏会成为你的最终幻想？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/c5034c4bfe414e58130d2c3bc2bae8f3.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/8a5a253fb883032edba85f313dfe91f2.poster.avif?t=1771980246\" width=780 height=249 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/8a5a253fb883032edba85f313dfe91f2.webm?t=1771980246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你会打造一款捕捉怪物的RPG游戏吗？ 一款温馨惬意的务农模拟游戏？ 又或者是一款充满魔力的动作冒险游戏？ 不管你要打造什么游戏，以你自己的方式来打造它——数以千计的物体、环境、角色和敌人供你随意选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在实时观察来访虚拟玩家进行探索的同时，布置每一颗树、打造每一项任务并决定玩家的职业类别。 如果他们难以为继则提高掉落率，或者增加敌人指标以让他们努力赚取经验值。 他们在你的世界里投入的时间越多，你的投资人就会越高兴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/841a2648854e26e2b31fb4f6f9ce8f15.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br>雇用测试者发现游戏中的小漏洞，或者随时跃入你的世界，通过玩家的眼睛体验你的杰作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/6be927a3ae1a8ed491d9ebffc0fff369.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计并打造你自己的MMO世界，让其成为虚拟玩家群体的聚集之地</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理游戏工作室的日常运营，从雇人和开人到让你的投资人开心</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过拓展你的世界、设计新任务和监控玩家旅程来吸引新虚拟玩家投身于你的MMO大作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推进战役进度以开发新物品、环境和机制，为你的创意赋予生机</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时测试游玩你的RPG，通过玩家的眼睛观察游戏世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由混搭任务风格以实现无尽的可复玩性</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用数以千计的物品进行个性化定制，或者自行设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与股东、员工、玩家和发布商进行艰难的沟通，做出将会影响工作室发展方向的有意义的选择。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/502cf9bde2da4c9db7f49daa8ee7f354.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/5f3098504f7d7c0ef4e795f75822c016.poster.avif?t=1771980246\" width=780 height=249 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/5f3098504f7d7c0ef4e795f75822c016.webm?t=1771980246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>创意模式相当于一个开放式沙盒，你可以撰写自己的故事、创造对话和过场画面、绘制角色以及调整游玩机制。 在网上浏览由其他人制作的游戏，或者在我们的内置游戏浏览器中上传你自己的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/c02665bc0cd5c410d511babcfc9c2fa9.webp?t=1771980246\" width=640 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/846520c35f8ba3e6884c1e86eb7c4f21.poster.avif?t=1771980246\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/846520c35f8ba3e6884c1e86eb7c4f21.webm?t=1771980246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯享建造模式是一种无压力、简化的体验，专注于最多 4 名玩家的共享创意控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单独或作为团队的一部分，构建完美的 RPG 世界，而无需承担经营游戏工作室的全部责任。从一系列随机生成的卡片中选择，以扩展和塑造你的世界，升级你的服务器以欢迎更多玩家，并解锁新的资源包。这个温馨、支持合作的模式让你专注于创造的纯粹乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/c82f5402c2b636b00bf0c83a59576689.poster.avif?t=1771980246\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365790/extras/c82f5402c2b636b00bf0c83a59576689.webm?t=1771980246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
